==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌmən|-ʌmən]]

===Transitive verb===
'''to summon'''

# to [[call]] people [[together]]; to [[convene]].
# to [[ask]] someone to [[come]]; to [[send for]].
#{{law}} to [[order]] someone to [[appear]] in court, especially by issueing a [[summons]].

